A simple example using the popular Flask package to create a web app that tracks
my progress through the #100DaysOfCode challenge. Modelled after the tutorial
provided at by Miguel Grinbgerg

Link: https://blog.miguelgrinberg.com/post/the-flask-mega-tutorial-part-ii-templates

Displays the README and file tree of all projects

To run:
    export FLASK_APP=microblog.py
    flask run

To visit the website, default address is: http://127.0.0.1:5000/
